headline: Three Reasons Why IEX is Risky and One Stock to Buy Instead
summary: IDEX has followed the market’s trajectory closely, rising in tandem with the S&P 500 over the past six months. The stock has climbed by 5.8% to $215 per share while the index has gained 6.1%.
